          .link-content
            %p
            Broker Bot automates the tedious (and unreliable) task of keeping track of communication between a real estate agent and his clients.  A copy of every email sent between broker and client is sent to the app, where it scans the email body for URLs referring to real estate listings.  If found, the app creates an entry for the new listing and pulls (scrapes) relevant data about the listing from the referring real estate website.
