              Physically mailed postcards are still an incredibly effictive way to communicate.  The Card-er-ator allows anyone to compose and mail a physical postcard from their mobile phone or browswer. After users select their card design and compose their message, a third party service prints and mails the card for a nominal fee.  Screenshots to come as the app is currently in development.
